### **4. 25_RealTimeGraphViewer**  
**Description:**  
A Python script that live-plots numeric values as a real-time line chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeGraphViewer - Live Numeric Data Charting

RealTimeGraphViewer makes it easy to visualize numeric data streams for sensors, simulations, or logs.

## Features
- Matplotlib line chart  
- Live streaming with smooth updates  
- Scrollable graph  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_RealTimeGraphViewer.git
cd 25_RealTimeGraphViewer
python visualize.py
